## OPE-301 Game Platform Management

### 1. Data Models ([src/types/game.ts](file:///c:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/%E7%87%9F%E9%81%8B%E5%BE%8C%E5%8F%B0/src/types/game.ts))
- **GameProvider**:
    - `id`: string (e.g., "PV-001")
    - `code`: string (e.g., "PG", "EVO")
    - `name`: string (e.g., "PG Soft")
    - `type`: 'SLOT' | 'LIVE' | 'SPORTS' | 'LOTTERY' | 'CARD'
    - `status`: 'ACTIVE' | 'DISABLED' | 'MAINTENANCE'
    - `sort_order`: number
    - `wallet_support`: 'CASH' | 'BONUS' | 'DUAL'
    - `last_operator`: string
    - `updated_at`: string

- **ProviderUpdateRequest**:
    - `status`?: 'ACTIVE' | 'DISABLED' | 'MAINTENANCE'
    - `sort_order`?: number
    - `reason`: string

